Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it. Hi, Doc. Hi, Don. Yes. I have a young friend that's an associate at work who is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:01:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cambodian, who was raised in the Buddhist traditions. Her mother died recently, and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,she immediately started getting what she thinks are things from the other side. She thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,her mother was trying to contact her, and now she's hearing voices, her father and her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,mother, carrying on conversations. And it's driving her nuts. She doesn't relate to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but it goes on in her head. Tell her she has the right to refuse it. Yes. And she has
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the right to demand entities cease and desist. Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, she's a Buddhist, you know, but she could try asking in the name of our Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ. I don't know what happens. Yeah. Well, could you use the Buddha? She, I told
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:02:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,her that I didn't think that they were her family, that it was most likely from the lower
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,realm. Well, it's entities taking advantage of the situation. Yes. See, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're emotional vulnerability. Yes. So they're trying to get her attention and get
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,involved with her. She should refuse them and say, get the ants. I hereby order you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave my presence. You don't have to say it in the name of Jesus Christ. You can just
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,say, I hereby order you to leave me alone and to leave my presence. Okay. She can demand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,them to leave. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a human, so you can demand that they leave. Human outranks them. I hereby order
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:03:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you to leave in the name of the Lord. They cannot refuse. That's it. Okay. She can order
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,them to leave. She can order them out because she actually has more power. Let's see. Since
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,she's a Buddhist, can she order them to leave? Wait a second. My answer was correct. She
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,has the karmic right to order them to leave. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She has the right to order them to leave or be. She does not have to cite the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for authority or just ... No, she doesn't have to cite the Buddha as authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spiritual reality, a spiritual reality. Just like the big dog has the right to order
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the little dog to stop nipping at his hind, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need the Buddha to give them an okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Picking order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She ranks up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. You're right. You're right. You're right. You're right. You're right. You're
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She ranks in the picking order. You know, it's quite involved to become a human as
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:04:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,low as we see human this gets. As far as what else goes on in the lower astral
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,realms, you know, we are very evolved. Even to have a sense of right or wrong, you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,know, is already... That's a gift to begin with. Yeah, yeah. Yeah. To be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,conceptualize and have a prefrontal cortex, yeah. That's an incredible gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm. And to understand that's even more incredible. Yeah, so I just tell her, you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,know, she has the right to demand them to leave her in peace. I will convey that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to her. Mm-hmm. I wanted to thank you also for responding to my email. Uh-huh. Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:05:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with that. It'll be fine. Yes, indeed it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have just two quick questions of what does Sedona calibrate as? A thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No. The town of Sedona? Uh-huh. From this beautiful surrounding. I don't know if we've done Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never done Sedona? I don't remember doing it, no. And also, you skipped a... Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. You skipped a dead white man. You didn't... What's dead white man? A 130 or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but what does that mean? Oh, you're not a literati, I see. Dead white man. To discredit the intellectual integrity in the history of mankind by relativism, you would then have to discredit that which, of course, you know, contradicts you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely. So you can belittle it by calling it, you know, the mad mouthings of dead white men or something. Something insulting, you know? Let's see if we got permission to do Sedona. We got permission to do Sedona. We got permission to do Sedona, is this? Oh. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about the difficulty and the courage required to be a human. After the last set, saying you went to the audience and you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:07:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoke with a lady who looks like was working through a big chunk of karma, was in a wheelchair, and you said to her, I think, all will be revealed at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Is that how this trip goes? We get a little explanation at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know. We all take the answer to that one with us, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I always wondered...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, in the sense that your life runs before you. Your whole life flashes before you. You're confronted with everything, every thought, every decision. Your life is reflected back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that kind of experience at the end transformative, maybe, in a sense, like a near death is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Near death is a dumb difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there such a disparity? It doesn't seem to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one's a rerun in which you can make choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The other, you don't have anything to say about it. You're leaving, so you're out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we know when we come down here? Are we given kind of like a preview of what we're signing up for, or are we just thrown in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you'd need to volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That would seem, in all justice and fairness, I don't know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all right, I can answer at a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have earned the karmic opportunity to make the choice, and then you have to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody is here by their own agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's here by their own agreement, so you can give up all the resentments, because the only reason you're here is because you said yes to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't know that it could be a big yes, or the details...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes is a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It means not to drag your feet kicking and screaming into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really have a question today, I just wanted to come up here to be, while you sign these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have enough to work on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a smart lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you aren't dead, you've got a lot to work on yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it keeps us busy, because each layer opens up to the next layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You finish with one layer, and suddenly, oops, about 22 lifetimes, you forgot. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:10:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These two are for my new lady love, Alaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a special signature for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Before my question, may I present you and Susan a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In November in Long Beach, I asked you about my running a fast marathon at a late age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said that the energy was good, so I really thank you very much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was a race director in January 2000, and I created a new race from scratch called the Malenathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the runners in my race got a free jacket, and I wanted to present you and Susan with one of the jackets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It says Malenathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, I see, oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, isn't that a fantastic run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll see you coming down the road there then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's going to run over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that the slogan is one race, one world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,One race, one world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Human race, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question pertains to Abraham Maslow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed that you have not calibrated Abraham Maslow in any of your books or your writings, and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're talking about peak experience psychologist, Maslow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Maslow described, he's a psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He described the so-called peak experience, transitory, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is whether you can calibrate Abraham Maslow, and also, I am writing a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,book on Abraham Maslow, and whether you can give me some guidance on that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because I'm not a student of Maslow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maslow's over 460, 480, 475, yeah, he's got to be in the high 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he described what's called peak experience, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way, a person gets a glimpse of their potentiality, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I never did give reference to him, because I hadn't really read Maslow at any
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who he is and what he taught, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was speaking of it as a psychological experience, you know, although a transcendental one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get some clarification on a couple of things that you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you've calibrated most of the countries of the West in the three and four hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And then earlier, you gave the calibration of Western civilization had fallen to 199.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you holding in mind the culture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In this lecture today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say it was 199.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that on the, we don't, was it on the?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,On the consciousness of Western civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what we said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We said what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We said what Western civilization was 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It is now 199 resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's now 199.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's reaffirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's below 200 now, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So Western civilization was around 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's been going down as you would assume by just watching the world to 199.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I was trying to understand a distinction between Western civilization, which is the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,world, and Western civilization, which is the human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Western civilization, which is the human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And Western civilization, which is the human, and Western civilization, which is the human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're trying to get more and more of the human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:14:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess I was trying to understand a distinction between Western civilization and the calibrations that you've given for most of the countries of the West being...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's all different countries, and there's America, and today, something new without, because what the Pope had said has to do with Western civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We never calibrated Western civilization as such, so we calibrated Western civilization for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we never calibrated Western civilization as such before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time here, so it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping you can help me with some clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a person that has a history of perversion with an arrest.
