Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A sexual perversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Has a sexual perversion, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,History.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
