Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:15:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you file a complaint with the licensing board of that person's profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
