Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You may pull up, they have a record.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was hard for me because I was feeling a lot of anger, and I was feeling very distracted, so I wasn't sure if I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it may put him out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You would have to decide how serious it was, and whether you think it's something that's done to others as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel that it's a pattern, this person's getting away with it right and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You could file a complaint with the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They can look into the matter.
