Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in charge of an institution, every three years, we had to have an FBI recheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:17:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to go to the FBI, get re-fingerprinted, and anything that was on your record in the last three years came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And in order to keep your position there, and the girls' school was there, so we had to get FBI clearance every three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'd be nice if they had something like that.
