Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs to be stopped because there's a lot of other women that they're afraid to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe you can find some of them and file a group complaint that would have more power
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,than just an isolated one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm working on, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
