Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to thank you and thank everybody here for this wonderful afternoon, and there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,was something I was having difficulty digesting with the use of the isms that you brought
