Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well the suffix ism brings whatever it is down to 190, because it now makes it a belief
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not truth, it's not reality, it's now a belief system, so you can have a belief
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,system in that which is false, and you can have a belief system make truth into a belief
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of the traps of the spiritual student, is he makes a belief system out of spiritual
