Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was curious, does that actually bring it down when you call it an ism as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it depends on how you mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm using its official title, not as a political positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted the clarity there, because I know there's a number of isms, like racism, it's
