Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:21:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a political viewpoint, when a thing becomes an ism, it tends to drop down, because
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,now it's a positionality, rather than intrinsically valid in its own right, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can make an ism out of that which is valid, in fact, and that brings it down.
