Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.19,0:26:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That entity, if you call it, can program thinking of other people
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.25,0:26:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and can program my physiological functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.73,0:26:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in other words, the negativity.
