Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.59,0:30:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to calibrate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.84,0:30:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's less than 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.46,0:30:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's less than 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.68,0:30:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she's so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.28,0:30:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would give up the book.
