Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.88,0:30:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.02,0:30:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting more confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.08,0:30:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.34,0:30:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate is less than 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.80,0:30:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he's the savior of the world...
