Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.76,0:31:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.04,0:32:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So I could be praying to Baba Gump Gump, and if my intention is good...
