Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.12,0:32:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's what matters most.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.94,0:32:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.08,0:32:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.14,0:32:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.86,0:32:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best that I pray to somebody that I know is integrous, being that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.86,0:32:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirmed level, yes, of higher consciousness, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.60,0:32:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
