Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.66,0:32:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty popular film.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.42,0:32:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to know what...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.12,0:32:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
