Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.13,0:32:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shawshank?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.93,0:32:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shawshank?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.48,0:32:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shawshank?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.52,0:32:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shawshank Redemption.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.16,0:32:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes place in the Second World War.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.82,0:32:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shawshank Redemption.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.40,0:32:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Redemption.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.10,0:32:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Redemption.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.28,0:33:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shawshank Redemption.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.72,0:33:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.90,0:33:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.28,0:33:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,400.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.73,0:33:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,395.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.88,0:33:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.48,0:33:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not intellectual.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.56,0:33:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.54,0:33:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.42,0:33:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.24,0:33:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.88,0:33:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I never watched movies, so I just wanted to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.96,0:33:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Dr. Hawkins, Mrs. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.87,0:33:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for allowing me to be in your presence today.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.97,0:33:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two books here that were like must-reads
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.82,0:33:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,when I started spiritual work back in the late 70s.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.20,0:33:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One is The Impersonal Life,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.08,0:33:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other one is The Life and Times,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.12,0:33:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Life and Teachings of the Masters of the Far East.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.80,0:33:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.78,0:33:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see, I don't think you've, in your books,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.22,0:33:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you haven't, you know, printed the calibration of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.96,0:33:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,if you have calibrated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.26,0:33:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you haven't calibrated them,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.92,0:33:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could calibrate them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.56,0:34:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is the one, you know, on the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.18,0:34:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is The Impersonal Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.96,0:34:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.10,0:34:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bremer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.92,0:34:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.42,0:34:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bremer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.19,0:34:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bremer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.05,0:34:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bremer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.63,0:34:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bremer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.49,0:34:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to do The Impersonal Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.49,0:34:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.85,0:34:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,300.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.44,0:34:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,290.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.82,0:34:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,295.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.04,0:34:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.48,0:34:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.14,0:34:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The other one, this is the volume one of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.36,0:34:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Life and Teachings of the Masters of the Far East.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.96,0:34:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a book of five volumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.78,0:34:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.58,0:34:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to do this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.03,0:34:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.39,0:34:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.95,0:34:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.17,0:34:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,295.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.17,0:34:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,300.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.15,0:34:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.34,0:34:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.58,0:34:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.26,0:34:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.06,0:34:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it's over 200, you said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.32,0:34:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.38,0:34:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one, it's the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.22,0:34:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the teacher himself, and then there's that which the person who's writing the book
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.08,0:34:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,says about the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.33,0:34:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't written by the teacher themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.71,0:34:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.63,0:34:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.19,0:35:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.59,0:35:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written by the teacher themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.51,0:35:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.67,0:35:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.43,0:35:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.87,0:35:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.24,0:35:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.54,0:35:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written by an author about the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.04,0:35:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.88,0:35:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.56,0:35:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.86,0:35:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.28,0:35:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One experience of-
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.88,0:35:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There are over 200, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.98,0:35:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.32,0:35:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One experience-
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.96,0:35:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.04,0:35:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking you've thrown your whole future in karmic inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.70,0:35:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.48,0:35:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't read these since.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.46,0:35:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Late 70s, but I'm reading your books now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.62,0:35:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but they're very well known, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.04,0:35:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.14,0:35:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real pleasure to be here in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.28,0:35:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very well known.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.74,0:35:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.88,0:35:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.77,0:35:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, 295 doesn't mean it is not as good as 400, because 295 is perfect when you're
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.27,0:35:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at 295, and then that leads you further.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.16,0:35:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been preparing a number of questions over the last few weeks, and most of them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.44,0:35:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,have been answered already.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.26,0:36:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I wanted to, including in the lineup this morning after 5 o'clock, talking within
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.42,0:36:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the holy company there, and how special it is to have, and feeling such an enormous amount
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.87,0:36:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,of gratitude for what you've brought in your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.26,0:36:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm honored by your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.13,0:36:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.41,0:36:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, could you give a little clarification on the grace of the teacher in respect to-
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.23,0:36:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.53,0:36:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.11,0:36:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace of a teacher and the openness of the student.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.71,0:36:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.33,0:36:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace of the teacher and the openness of the student.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.71,0:36:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.99,0:37:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a little clarification on that, a little explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.13,0:37:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need clarification on?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.19,0:37:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well-
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.43,0:37:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's self-evident.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.33,0:37:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.77,0:37:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the question was, because I started psychotherapy, like you mentioned, about a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.45,0:37:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,week ago, and before coming here, she- this is my first time here from 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.71,0:37:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And she said, what are you going to expect by going?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.93,0:37:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.17,0:37:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just drawn to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.52,0:37:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And after reading your books for three years and watching your DVDs, I was just told to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.02,0:37:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,get an airline ticket and be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.38,0:37:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.24,0:37:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.62,0:37:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fulfilling an important thing, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.66,0:37:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.74,0:37:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to pick up the specific energy itself on top of the words and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.32,0:37:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.94,0:37:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.60,0:37:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.90,0:37:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.00,0:37:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleveland, Ohio.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.02,0:37:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.80,0:37:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.80,0:37:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.00,0:37:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.32,0:37:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.70,0:37:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad weather back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.96,0:37:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.96,0:37:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.64,0:37:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.14,0:37:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Last weekend, three feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.02,0:37:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Three feet of snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.74,0:37:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.10,0:37:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.50,0:37:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.36,0:37:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.38,0:37:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad weather, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.20,0:38:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.16,0:38:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.61,0:38:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.54,0:38:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.18,0:38:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.78,0:38:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to submit something to a Sundance workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.37,0:38:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'd like to know if there's a difference between the festival and the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.65,0:38:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.67,0:38:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.59,0:38:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a workshop that the Sundance, there's no difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.33,0:38:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.31,0:38:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The last workshop calibrated pretty low.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.01,0:38:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The organization calibrates over 200, which is 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.47,0:38:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's iffy, iffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.17,0:38:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's iffy, could go either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.62,0:38:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it might be right at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.96,0:38:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.90,0:39:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if they choose certain films this year, it goes down, and if they choose these films,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.18,0:39:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.61,0:39:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.97,0:39:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.71,0:39:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.01,0:39:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.13,0:39:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.19,0:39:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.33,0:39:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.37,0:39:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, maybe there's no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.30,0:39:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a workshop where they help writers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.10,0:39:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.38,0:39:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they help writers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.26,0:39:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.64,0:39:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.92,0:39:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.12,0:39:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking three different questions now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.79,0:39:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask about the workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.15,0:39:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The workshop exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.05,0:39:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The workshop, which is what you're referring to, calibrates over 200, exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.34,0:39:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.78,0:39:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.78,0:39:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have one other question.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.08,0:39:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know if you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.56,0:39:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to be better at sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.36,0:39:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.54,0:39:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something I've been working on for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.82,0:39:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Be better at what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.98,0:39:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.74,0:39:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.97,0:39:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give me some advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.24,0:40:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's tempting to want to control it, hold on to it, you know, make something happen with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.88,0:40:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't try to let go of controlling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.78,0:40:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Notice that you want control.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.92,0:40:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.16,0:40:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let go of wanting to control it, and then let go of controlling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.09,0:40:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.31,0:40:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it's not the control.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.71,0:40:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your desire to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.99,0:40:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your desire to control things, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.13,0:40:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, you think there's a secret benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.57,0:40:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah, you're willing to give up the secret benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.87,0:40:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I control this, then I'll be happier and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.79,0:40:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.46,0:40:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it isn't the control.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.76,0:40:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you think it's going to bring about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.14,0:40:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.70,0:40:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be successful, wealthy, happy, et cetera, good-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.52,0:40:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let go of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.88,0:40:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.00,0:40:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it all your life and still be bad-looking, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.59,0:40:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be good at being bad-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.12,0:40:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is there a way to...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.20,0:40:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll be an ugly, don't bother you no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.30,0:40:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See, folks out in front get the brunt, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.90,0:40:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.26,0:40:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.18,0:41:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do that, really, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.69,0:41:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, do you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.23,0:41:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.69,0:41:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.75,0:41:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you just, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.09,0:41:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got through telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.39,0:41:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but it's hard to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.65,0:41:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to listen to the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.70,0:41:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You think there's going to be some magical benefit,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.68,0:41:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so you have to let go wanting that benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.19,0:41:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn it over to the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.13,0:41:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're hooked on some magical benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.87,0:41:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.02,0:41:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.46,0:41:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.06,0:41:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that you want to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.44,0:41:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.32,0:41:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want is some hidden benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.32,0:41:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.14,0:41:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.72,0:41:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.14,0:41:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the benefit over to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.72,0:41:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're supposed to be rich, you'll be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.14,0:41:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're supposed to be poor, you'll be poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.80,0:41:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.10,0:41:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.96,0:41:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm unhappy both ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.76,0:41:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.59,0:41:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're poor, you eat better, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.63,0:41:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.97,0:41:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor, you eat better.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.65,0:42:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're poor, you eat better?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.53,0:42:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're poor, you don't eat as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.79,0:42:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You said when you're poor, you eat better.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.11,0:42:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean when you're rich, you eat better.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.97,0:42:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.37,0:42:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're poor, you appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.71,0:42:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A hot dog is a feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.65,0:42:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.97,0:42:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just really happy to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.45,0:42:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.75,0:42:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.41,0:42:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And your work has just been a total guiding force in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.41,0:42:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for the past year and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.91,0:42:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.39,0:42:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been following many of the recommendations in the books
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.07,0:42:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and been doing the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.85,0:42:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.63,0:42:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And as...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.75,0:42:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of my growth, I also did this workshop
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.05,0:42:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that was in the lineage of Est,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.89,0:42:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,like the old Est workshops.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.87,0:42:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a rerun of the Essence of Est?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.27,0:42:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.81,0:42:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good old Warner's...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.93,0:42:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.37,0:42:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it proved to be the most devastating experience of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.51,0:42:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, devastating.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.03,0:42:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it devastating?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.80,0:42:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.32,0:43:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It started off very much responsibility, integrity...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.22,0:43:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.46,0:43:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.48,0:43:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And very non-judgmental.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.98,0:43:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.56,0:43:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Accepting freedom of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.06,0:43:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And as it progressed with this other facilitator,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.36,0:43:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it got very harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.14,0:43:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt very...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.60,0:43:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The facilitator was extremely frustrated and felt very angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.88,0:43:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was in a place of being really open and trusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.38,0:43:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.16,0:43:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.84,0:43:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, being surrounded by a room full of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.67,0:43:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,saying the most harshest things they could say about me personally...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.93,0:43:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.39,0:43:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...in an effort to, like, break me through to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.87,0:43:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.71,0:43:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.97,0:43:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.01,0:43:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But part of my struggle has been knowing whether...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.15,0:44:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I want to know what is true, and I want to be in integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.81,0:44:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that whole process was in integrity,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.81,0:44:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had such...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.97,0:44:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I had such hard time with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.45,0:44:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,am I having difficulty confronting something,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.13,0:44:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,or was the workshop just...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.20,0:44:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it you or the trainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.78,0:44:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.74,0:44:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.08,0:44:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.47,0:44:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.98,0:44:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the trainer, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.02,0:44:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.72,0:44:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not all enlightened Buddhas, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.15,0:44:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Werner himself fell on his butt, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.61,0:44:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.79,0:44:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a really important treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.49,0:44:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, now, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.47,0:44:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain value to it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.95,0:44:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go of the facades, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.13,0:44:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can remember when he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.61,0:44:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,he's this little old lady in a wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.15,0:44:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.53,0:44:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,how about getting off your crippled little old lady in a wheelchair act?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.79,0:44:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that depends on how you hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.19,0:44:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.89,0:44:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That would sound sadistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.07,0:45:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, it blew the lady right out of her wheelchair,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.11,0:45:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and she quit the little sick old lady in the wheelchair act.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.25,0:45:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.47,0:45:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.07,0:45:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.59,0:45:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.13,0:45:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.43,0:45:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she was a nasty little old lady on crutches.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.42,0:45:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you had a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.50,0:45:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a benefit out of it, even though you don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.50,0:45:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing the Werner trip is part of the initiation, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.10,0:45:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.92,0:45:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. David, I've got to really commend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.17,0:45:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I love your humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.69,0:45:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.11,0:45:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that is just outstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.93,0:45:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of the things,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.31,0:46:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been chasing this path about as long as you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.51,0:46:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been stumbling, I think, more.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.89,0:46:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm still out in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.95,0:46:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I figure I've gotten onto Jacob's ladder,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.95,0:46:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know how many rungs I've stepped.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.15,0:46:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to check with you and see if I've passed 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.91,0:46:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody, you wouldn't be asking if you were under 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.54,0:46:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.49,0:46:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give me a number or is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.85,0:46:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he wants to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.38,0:46:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.68,0:46:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.88,0:46:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.22,0:46:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,395.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.42,0:46:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,400.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.52,0:46:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, 395 is a very good energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.76,0:46:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.44,0:46:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.04,0:46:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And that kind of energy will take you the rest of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.67,0:46:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enthusiasm, commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.54,0:46:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.30,0:46:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick-to-itiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.22,0:46:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I feel I'm running in that field,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.86,0:47:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know where to head
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.56,0:47:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to where I can take this talent to help serve the Supreme Being.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.60,0:47:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel I'm still searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.80,0:47:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're serving the Supreme Being
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.46,0:47:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,by just struggling to fulfill your own karmic possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.16,0:47:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's serving God to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.08,0:47:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Become all that you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.57,0:47:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, from 395, I would work on lovingness then.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.93,0:47:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got willingness, you've got enthusiasm, you've got commitment, you've got loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.51,0:47:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got everything you need to rebuild the world, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.33,0:47:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would choose something devotional then and jump the 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.15,0:47:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a lot of book reading, and jump right into the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.47,0:47:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can catapult from 395 to 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.77,0:47:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.47,0:47:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.69,0:47:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to have a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.19,0:47:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a picture, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.17,0:48:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.25,0:48:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.97,0:48:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.73,0:48:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Try one more here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.95,0:48:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you the one that was in the same area that he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.23,0:48:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was on the tanker.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.80,0:48:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He was on a tanker, and I was on a mine sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.50,0:48:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.32,0:48:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We were playing the same war.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.16,0:48:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't tear up the bars in Singapore, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.66,0:48:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.26,0:48:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.30,0:48:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.08,0:48:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.76,0:48:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shanghai.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.38,0:48:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shanghai.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.74,0:48:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shanghai.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.70,0:48:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I knew it was one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.26,0:48:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.62,0:48:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.52,0:48:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.81,0:48:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Singapore is a very strict place.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.45,0:48:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They like them looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.59,0:48:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.01,0:48:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shanghai.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.67,0:48:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.57,0:48:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My question, I have watched your DVDs on health,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.41,0:48:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was really glued to the one that said that you were only able to eat lettuce at a certain time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.43,0:48:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Practically down to eating lettuce.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.09,0:48:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.63,0:48:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been that way myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.93,0:49:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was diagnosed with fibromyalgia,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.09,0:49:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've been told all different kinds of things to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.91,0:49:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally, when I was so exasperated and down to lettuce and one grain from India,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.09,0:49:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,like you said in your DVD,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.51,0:49:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched your DVDs, and then I ordered a couple of more.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.15,0:49:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I got that not labeling it mentally and saying I am an infinite being and I am not subject to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.07,0:49:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.09,0:49:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby refuse it and don't accept it and choose instead to love myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.21,0:49:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got that it's unconscious guilt, and I'm really trying to do that and do it and do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.09,0:49:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and I still feel the symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.43,0:49:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And so now I'm getting into, I'm doing it wrong, you know, I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.17,0:49:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and don't forget it took me years to overcome those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.37,0:49:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I just didn't get it on Monday, I was healed by Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.37,0:49:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.13,0:49:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of those things, I had them for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.71,0:49:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.21,0:49:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And it maybe took me a couple of years to evolve out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.21,0:49:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, like you said, two years for hypoglycemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.51,0:49:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it took you two years for hypoglycemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.61,0:49:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a number of them took some years.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.77,0:49:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.27,0:49:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was just wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.77,0:50:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Some went instantly, but I was in a very unique sort of state of consciousness at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.62,0:50:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them went very quickly, others took years, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.72,0:50:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering if you could give me any more advice, because I just get, I'm starting
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.80,0:50:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to kind of go down and feel like, oh, I can't do this, or I'll never get out of, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.40,0:50:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get out of all those positive things I've been doing after watching the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.44,0:50:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's because you're doing them to try and control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.78,0:50:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.94,0:50:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do them for their own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.58,0:50:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.38,0:50:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an infinite being, I'm only subject to what I hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.66,0:50:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what you hold in mind is either personal, or because...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.98,0:50:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.08,0:50:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.14,0:50:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it could be collective.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.14,0:50:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.14,0:50:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of the major ailments I've had in the last few years are not things that I hold
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.30,0:50:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in mind personally as even a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.82,0:50:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.82,0:50:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are certainly out there in the collective.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.38,0:50:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.51,0:50:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can buy them in, so therefore, maybe for karmic reasons, you buy something in
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.71,0:50:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,from the collective, and it takes some time to undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.65,0:50:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.65,0:51:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, for God's help in the matter, forgive yourself for having it, and, uh, yeah, I think
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.72,0:51:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that, uh, within a certain karmic period of time, it will, uh, leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.72,0:51:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.72,0:51:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.85,0:51:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I always feel like you've got a cash register.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.85,0:51:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, they used to register pain in terms of doles, D-O-L-S.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.85,0:51:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.85,0:51:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is 250 doles.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.85,0:51:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How many doles have I paid in migraine headaches?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.85,0:51:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,149.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.85,0:51:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe I only got 48 doles to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.85,0:51:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden, out came Emitrex, one of my biggest...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.85,0:51:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.85,0:51:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.85,0:51:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.01,0:51:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.01,0:51:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.01,0:51:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.01,0:51:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.01,0:51:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.10,0:51:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.10,0:51:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.10,0:51:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.10,0:51:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.10,0:51:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.23,0:51:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.23,0:51:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.23,0:51:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.23,0:51:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.23,0:51:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.23,0:51:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.23,0:51:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.23,0:51:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.23,0:51:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.23,0:51:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.86,0:51:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.86,0:51:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.86,0:51:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I battled migraine my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.86,0:51:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.86,0:51:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing cured it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.86,0:51:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.86,0:51:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a chiropractor in town that could fix it, but then he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.86,0:51:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.82,0:51:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.95,0:51:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.95,0:52:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what the total, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.64,0:52:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.64,0:52:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a karmic debt of a certain amount of suffering, and if it don't take this form,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.10,0:52:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it will take another form.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.38,0:52:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And so maybe something like that goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.46,0:52:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.46,0:52:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.08,0:52:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.08,0:52:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so. Maybe you have a certain amount of suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.22,0:52:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and if it doesn't take this form, it can take
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.98,0:52:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,another form. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.90,0:52:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.60,0:52:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. You haven't got a toothache, you've got a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.84,0:52:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If that didn't do what happened, you got an attack of the gallbladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.88,0:52:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it wanders around.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.00,0:52:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the amount of suffering you've
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.88,0:52:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,brought others. Okay. So that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.62,0:52:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,suffered out is the equivalent to the suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.68,0:52:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you've brought into the life of others. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.62,0:52:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. So that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.86,0:52:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,takes away the resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.86,0:52:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of my questions I asked you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.12,0:52:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.68,0:52:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.66,0:52:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.93,0:52:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,do we have to pay that back?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.13,0:52:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.93,0:53:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc. I just want to sit with you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.07,0:53:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a moment. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.22,0:53:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm. Haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.72,0:53:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Haven't seen you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.98,0:53:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in a while. When's your last month?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.38,0:53:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.60,0:53:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Every month is a while, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.90,0:53:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Two months is a while-while.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.96,0:53:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.86,0:53:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.77,0:53:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you walk a while in your brother's shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.16,0:53:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.98,0:53:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.48,0:53:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.06,0:53:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.90,0:53:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.90,0:53:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.56,0:53:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.20,0:53:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.70,0:53:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.76,0:53:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering, a couple of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.42,0:53:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One was, I was wondering, in AA, they have a group of people who get pretty fussy about
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.46,0:53:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the big book. They refer to them as kind of big book thumpers. And they get a little grumpy
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.50,0:53:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,about the treatment centers.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.02,0:53:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.52,0:53:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.02,0:53:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.32,0:53:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.82,0:53:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.32,0:53:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're not really interested in the treatment centers and things like that. And
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.82,0:53:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know what your thoughts were on that particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.82,0:54:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a naïve attitude. You know, AA has no position on outside matters. So it's
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.82,0:54:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,inappropriate to have a viewpoint on the treatment modalities, centers, hospitals, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.82,0:54:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.82,0:54:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,AA has no opinion on outside issues. So I would call them to mind to respect that tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.24,0:54:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other thing that comes up for me, a couple of times in your lectures, I've had
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.08,0:54:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.08,0:54:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.28,0:54:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.26,0:54:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very nice experience where, like, the top of my head, I feel like it opens
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.10,0:54:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,up a little bit. And I just, I have some bliss, very pleasurable. And there have been a variety
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.12,0:54:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of other experiences like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.54,0:54:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.76,0:54:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, lately, I still find myself in a state of doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.64,0:54:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A state of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.04,0:54:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.60,0:54:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.10,0:54:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.58,0:54:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A significant doubt about sometimes just Kinesiology. Sometimes, the teachings. Sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.52,0:54:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,God in general. Just kind of this deep, nagging doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.58,0:54:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.44,0:54:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.92,0:55:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so I just wanted to know, get your thoughts on that too, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.76,0:55:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll transcend that also.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.68,0:55:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what the doubt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.86,0:55:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the doubt that you trust your own mind to the degree that it interferes with your belief in something higher?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.76,0:55:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that's it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.26,0:55:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of trust in my own mind, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.44,0:55:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are genuflecting to your own mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.64,0:55:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, mighty mind. Oh, great guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.06,0:55:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the doubt of dubiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.44,0:55:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's narcissus.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.70,0:55:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's narcissus.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.94,0:55:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always just narcissism, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.00,0:55:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.43,0:55:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.22,0:55:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel guilty about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.06,0:56:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel guilty about it in being narcissistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.48,0:56:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.02,0:56:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just punish yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.76,0:56:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.70,0:56:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doubt is its own punishment, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.42,0:56:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.76,0:56:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're agonizing yourself with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.74,0:56:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I doubt a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.74,0:56:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, doubt creates a lot of anxiety, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.90,0:56:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't get run over by a car until you make up your mind one way or the other, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.88,0:56:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.88,0:56:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.88,0:56:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I really, I love you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.88,0:56:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.88,0:56:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.88,0:56:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.88,0:56:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you're going the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.88,0:56:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're hitting resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.88,0:56:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ego doesn't want to let go of that, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.88,0:56:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.88,0:56:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.56,0:56:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, they want to surrender its sovereignty.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.56,0:56:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.56,0:56:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm mostly here because I've been afraid to come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.20,0:56:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to thank you both for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.20,0:56:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.20,0:56:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.48,0:56:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.99,0:56:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.26,0:56:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.26,0:56:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.26,0:56:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.26,0:57:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.64,0:57:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.64,0:57:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.64,0:57:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.85,0:57:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.85,0:57:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.85,0:57:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.85,0:57:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God for the opportunity to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.85,0:57:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.85,0:57:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I was standing in line, I've been doing A Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.20,0:57:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is my second pass through.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.20,0:57:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time, it was like I had on rose-colored glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.20,0:57:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was wondrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.20,0:57:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And the second time through has been like the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.33,0:57:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.33,0:57:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, difficult, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.33,0:57:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been having trouble with meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.33,0:57:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at the point in the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.33,0:57:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing some meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.33,0:57:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,where you're asked to meditate for five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.15,0:57:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.55,0:57:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And five minutes isn't very much,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.51,0:57:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but my mind will not be still.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.13,0:57:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I get these little flashes of, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.61,0:57:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,little pictures that have nothing to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.65,0:57:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.97,0:57:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, create an image of that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.09,0:58:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,which is most aligned with what the lesson is.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.36,0:58:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If it says forgiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.94,0:58:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,picture yourself forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.94,0:58:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture one of the great saints forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.92,0:58:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.83,0:58:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it that crawled all the way on his knees
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.99,0:58:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to beg the pardon of, what was it,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.33,0:58:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the pope or the emperor or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.19,0:58:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just picture something and be that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.01,0:58:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.04,0:58:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.82,0:58:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you give yourself a visualization to work with
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.38,0:58:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.34,0:58:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise you just have a mentalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.45,0:58:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.08,0:58:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a little, like a little revelation
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.88,0:58:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was standing in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.04,0:58:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of one of the lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.52,0:58:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,was...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.26,0:58:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This past week was that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.26,0:58:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'm afraid of...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.02,0:58:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fear God,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.76,0:58:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'm afraid of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.06,0:58:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of God and you're afraid of joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.08,0:58:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.54,0:58:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.56,0:58:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of one of the lessons, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.28,0:59:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To fear God is to be afraid of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.70,0:59:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And it occurred to me
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.82,0:59:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that being afraid to come up here
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.22,0:59:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is being afraid of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.41,0:59:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.69,0:59:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.84,0:59:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.24,0:59:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've got the courage to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.64,0:59:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.10,0:59:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.46,0:59:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both the back of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.86,0:59:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.98,0:59:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurie Asko.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.27,0:59:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.24,0:59:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.12,0:59:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.92,0:59:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to get up in front of an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.70,0:59:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.74,0:59:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.16,0:59:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.06,0:59:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to get up in front of an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.14,0:59:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.93,0:59:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.97,0:59:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to get up in front of an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.51,0:59:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the right distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.95,0:59:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,First time I did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.95,0:59:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to have cardiac arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.92,0:59:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.88,0:59:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.04,0:59:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to say I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.02,1:00:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm deeply grateful for your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.86,1:00:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And for your devotion to your students.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.22,1:00:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly inspires me
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.00,1:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to be the best that I can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.54,1:00:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.74,1:00:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.02,1:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is about
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.80,1:00:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,staying in unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.80,1:00:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in today's world.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.84,1:00:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.40,1:00:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I tend to...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.66,1:00:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's my heart's desire, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.68,1:00:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I tend to run into people
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.32,1:00:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that are not of the same level of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.68,1:00:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.72,1:00:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.74,1:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you had any specific advice
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.20,1:00:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in staying in my integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.84,1:00:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.62,1:00:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in staying in unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.42,1:00:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a great deal of spiritual effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.88,1:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.26,1:00:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.16,1:00:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To try to stay with the essence of things
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.08,1:00:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and not perception.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.68,1:00:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And not to have an opinion
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.04,1:00:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,or a viewpoint about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.16,1:00:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And that requires, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.50,1:00:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you're really almost years of inner work.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.84,1:00:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.60,1:00:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask God for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.70,1:00:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you're doing the course?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.48,1:00:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.92,1:01:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not presently.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.77,1:01:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask to see the miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.95,1:01:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of seeing the situation in truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.55,1:01:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in the eyes of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.06,1:01:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask to see the essence and not the appearance.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.54,1:01:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.61,1:01:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.75,1:01:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All beings are intrinsically divine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.69,1:01:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just some are more divine than others.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.54,1:01:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what you see is the intrinsic innocence
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.02,1:01:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of the child within each person.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.24,1:01:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see within each,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.02,1:01:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is the innocence of the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.51,1:01:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the most horrific being
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.35,1:01:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is being so
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.35,1:01:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the naivete
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.79,1:01:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of the child within.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.43,1:01:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.35,1:01:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.60,1:01:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.20,1:01:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,profound stupidity is what's under it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.86,1:02:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, profound blindness and ignorance, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.83,1:02:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So you eventually have compassion
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.79,1:02:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,for they really do not know what they do, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.78,1:02:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And love them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.20,1:02:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to like them,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.78,1:02:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can quit hating them, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.42,1:02:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can feel sorry for them, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.56,1:02:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.48,1:02:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.62,1:02:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha recommended compassion
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.64,1:02:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,towards all things at all times, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.53,1:02:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.78,1:02:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why before the headsman chops your head off,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.44,1:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you tell him, don't feel bad about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.04,1:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just your job.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.94,1:02:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel bad about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.48,1:02:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing your duty to the crown, to the king.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.01,1:02:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And in business dealings,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.67,1:02:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,when you discover someone is not of integrity,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.23,1:02:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume it's best to just disassociate from those.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.41,1:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look, 50% of the world that you're going to meet in America
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.21,1:02:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is below the level of 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.93,1:02:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.82,1:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to some other places on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.62,1:03:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,about 90% are going to be below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.64,1:03:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You better get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.98,1:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.38,1:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually you see there are ducks quacking at your ankles.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.40,1:03:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good perspective.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.12,1:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.72,1:03:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Love and blessings to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.80,1:03:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.20,1:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.88,1:03:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we say,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.64,1:03:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,don't ducks quacking at their ankles, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.44,1:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.94,1:03:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.90,1:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, ducks quacking at your ankles.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.08,1:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.02,1:03:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been having some spiritual experiences,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.98,1:03:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can just describe them as blowouts,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.44,1:03:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,where I feel it first happened when I met you,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.36,1:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I started experiencing cities,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.84,1:04:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.54,1:04:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the hairs on my body stood up on end,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.58,1:04:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I went to a,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.56,1:04:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I closed my eyes and went to a state of peacefulness.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.98,1:04:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And this,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.42,1:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but afterwards my body felt floppy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.38,1:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And floppy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.42,1:04:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it was just,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.66,1:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it happened,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.72,1:04:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the last time it happened,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.18,1:04:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt really sick afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.62,1:04:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that normal?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.20,1:04:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's phenomenal.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.74,1:04:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.74,1:04:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to come and go,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.74,1:04:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're on a spiritual pathway.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.74,1:04:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be very sudden and transitory,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.66,1:04:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and nobody really knows what they mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.66,1:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just energy feels coming up, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.18,1:04:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.18,1:04:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.18,1:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're moving along.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.18,1:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.18,1:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.18,1:04:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.18,1:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stirring the waters.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.18,1:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.52,1:04:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and lots of people are waiting for you to come to England as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.58,1:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a big group waiting for you to come over.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.58,1:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.58,1:05:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people are waiting for you to come to England.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.58,1:05:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, England.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.58,1:05:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.58,1:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.58,1:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a big group.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.58,1:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still there?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.58,1:05:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just about.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.58,1:05:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just about.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.58,1:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.58,1:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my ancestors back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.58,1:05:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.71,1:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.71,1:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question on what you were saying earlier about activism.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.71,1:05:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering, is the best position to take one of non-action?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.38,1:05:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.79,1:05:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
