Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.64,1:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahatma Gandhi.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.64,1:06:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So to be unconditionally loving towards everyone,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.94,1:06:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,even though you disagree with them,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.46,1:06:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is more powerful than anything you can actually do in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.78,1:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what you are, what you have become,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.02,1:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that influences and raises the level of the water
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.70,1:06:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and that lifts all the ships out at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.50,1:06:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so focus on ourselves is the best way to solve any problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.41,1:06:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.15,1:06:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.49,1:06:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To focus on ourselves as a way to solve any other problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.99,1:06:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To become all that you can be for its own sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.27,1:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.15,1:06:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you become loving towards all of life,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.34,1:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're radiating an energy which is quite powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.46,1:06:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not many people even reach 540, 4% of the population.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.34,1:06:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.20,1:07:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already beyond 96% of the population.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.72,1:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,540 unconditional love is extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.18,1:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.14,1:07:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So to become unconditionally loving is already doing what you can for the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.53,1:07:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.07,1:07:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people at 540 does more for the world than 10,000 people on a peace march.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.37,1:07:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Calabrese at 180 with the cops and the police dogs and the hoses and, you know, the riot police.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.77,1:07:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.75,1:07:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.37,1:07:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,See, force creates counterforce.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.87,1:07:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Power, there's nothing that can go against power.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.77,1:07:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.55,1:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you walk around radiating love and geniality and good humor and goodwill towards people,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.27,1:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing they can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.89,1:07:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I had your mercy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.49,1:07:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't even call the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.21,1:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. She was kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.05,1:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the kindness police.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.35,1:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.99,1:08:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. If you see the wisdom of God, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.35,1:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.01,1:08:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahatma Gandhi, that was what he recommended.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.13,1:08:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Be all that you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.67,1:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.27,1:08:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.83,1:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.99,1:08:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.44,1:08:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for today's lecture about standing up for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.81,1:08:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question was about Mahatma Gandhi, and you answered the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.20,1:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What I wanted to say was whenever I come up here, I feel like my ego gets a good beating.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.58,1:08:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.16,1:08:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.52,1:08:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,After I come here and I go back,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.88,1:09:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, there's so much happening,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.12,1:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I guess the burning of karma, whatever you call it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.77,1:09:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.13,1:09:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.54,1:09:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My ego gets a beating.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.22,1:09:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.70,1:09:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.34,1:09:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I also loved what you said about standing up for truth
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.80,1:09:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and was wondering about, since being with you,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.91,1:09:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,coming into your field, yours and wonderful Susan's field,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.20,1:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and the attraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.18,1:09:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, being in the attraction field with you and loving that,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.51,1:09:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the same as knowing that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.67,1:09:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in the attraction field and knowing that, is that the same?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.92,1:10:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.93,1:10:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.48,1:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Repeat the question, but don't go so close to the mic.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.58,1:10:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.28,1:10:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.97,1:10:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Being attracted to you as my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.67,1:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.25,1:10:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.41,1:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And being in that field.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.93,1:10:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.89,1:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And moving forward in that, loving that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.57,1:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.89,1:10:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the same as knowing that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.52,1:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it takes you to knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.72,1:10:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some degree of knowingness is what makes you select the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.43,1:10:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.39,1:10:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But then it takes you to your own knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.65,1:10:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that within you is the source of knowingness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.71,1:10:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-verbal awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.04,1:10:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.40,1:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I'm standing up for what I know,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.58,1:10:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and standing up for the truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.40,1:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.40,1:10:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the same as standing with you in your field?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.40,1:10:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In a certain symbolic way, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.40,1:10:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.40,1:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.40,1:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.08,1:10:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.08,1:10:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't quite get the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.08,1:10:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.08,1:10:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hartzler.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.08,1:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.88,1:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.58,1:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.82,1:11:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.82,1:11:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wanted to come and express gratitude and be in the presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.82,1:11:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.82,1:11:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And say hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.82,1:11:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.82,1:11:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.82,1:11:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.82,1:11:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.82,1:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.82,1:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.82,1:11:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.82,1:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You usually have some really good questions that I would like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.82,1:11:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.82,1:11:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.82,1:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.23,1:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.23,1:11:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.23,1:11:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.23,1:11:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.39,1:11:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.72,1:11:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.71,1:11:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.71,1:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.71,1:11:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to come up for their benefit.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.71,1:11:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.79,1:11:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to come up.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.79,1:11:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She had nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.79,1:11:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to say nothing into the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.79,1:11:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.79,1:12:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody can say something.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.79,1:12:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot harder to say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.79,1:12:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.79,1:12:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.79,1:12:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
