Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.16,1:17:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,happen. I really wanted to sit here and be very self-conscious in front of you. Yes, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.28,1:17:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Conscious of self, I know. You know, you're doing fine with it. It's like trying to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.75,1:17:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,catch yourself in the mirror. By the time you turn around to catch yourself in the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.07,1:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you're gone, you see. This is not writing very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.52,1:18:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you have expressed joy when people's lives fall apart upon meeting you, and my life was
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.61,1:18:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,already falling apart, so I can't say that you had a part of that. However, I've had to rewrite
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.03,1:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this book about four times, and you've had a big piece of that. Oh, thank you. Oh, thank you. Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.45,1:18:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the dedication in there is to you, and I've also endorsed it. And you have talked about playing
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.31,1:18:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,magic and being magic, and I wanted to present you with some magic wands, because every magician
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.71,1:19:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,needs a magic wand, and these will transform water and increase hydration. Yes. And perhaps
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.09,1:19:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,supposedly also increase absorption of minerals, and there's some information in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.45,1:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. And I do have available the studies, but I don't have a printer, it's in storage. Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.55,1:19:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can email the files if you so desire. Thank you very much. Thank you. Thank you. Thank you for your
