Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.20,1:19:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry, yes. Okay. The walls in sheep's clothing? Yes. And you said it's like one of the
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.29,1:19:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,traditions to betray and rape the heart of the innocent child. Yes. And I wanted to know if you
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.23,1:20:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,could tell me something, maybe how to forgive this. How to what? How to forgive. How to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.32,1:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, forgive the rapist? Yeah, or oneself. Yeah, forgive the rapist for being an animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.35,1:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's spiritual rapists that are worse than physical rapists. There's one in the newspaper, right, in the
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.82,1:20:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,newspaper, that says, you know, you can't take away your money, take away your integrity, take away your
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.12,1:20:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,relationships, completely own the person. Yeah. So how can you forgive that, is what you're asking?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.02,1:20:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Yeah, the person themself is the victim of the narcissistic ego. The person themself is the victim
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.52,1:21:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of evil. They have surrendered, sold out to the devil, so now they need compassion. If you knew the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.41,1:21:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,future of someone like me, it would be a different story. But you don't have to have compassion. You're
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.41,1:21:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but he was sold out for the devil.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.19,1:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You would see what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.88,1:21:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.99,1:21:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And how would you best undo that?
