Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.18,1:21:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's their negative karma to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.24,1:21:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yours to learn, to discern appearance from essence.
