Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.88,1:25:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With look a behavior that is, if you're in a called Extra statements.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.98,1:25:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanguations come from.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.16,1:25:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the glamorization and perception onto it Ramana Maharishi says there's no point
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.47,1:26:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to try and save the world you see because the world you see doesn't even
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.59,1:26:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,exist yeah all right so it has to be understood in the context in which it is
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.78,1:26:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,set so at 700 that is obvious at 150 that sounds like absurdity see so you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.96,1:26:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,stay with that which makes sense to you and maybe stretches a little bit but not
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.70,1:26:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,too far out of where you yourself are how you see the world is a projection of
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.40,1:26:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,perception that's what relativism is relativism even denies that there is
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.59,1:26:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,such things in reality that nothing is everything is nothing but perception
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.27,1:26:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the sophistry of narcissism no there is an essence to things and there
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.06,1:26:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is an appearance and to differentiate between
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.22,1:27:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the two yep that's what socrates taught yep okay I hope that answers your
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.66,1:27:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,question for her thank you so much it does tell you Socrates had the answer
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.07,1:27:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,okay ain't it so soggy yeah yeah thank you sometimes we call him Socrates I
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.55,1:27:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,just wanted to say thank you like so many people here today
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.52,1:27:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.92,1:27:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,made it a no call you too but I'm glad I could come into this discussion today thank you so much I just wanted to say thank you like so many people here today I
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.02,1:27:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to say thank you like so many people here today I
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.06,1:27:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,reading and listening and praying and trying to do the best I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.22,1:27:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.12,1:27:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all anybody can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.64,1:27:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.16,1:27:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We already have a picture. Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.48,1:27:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.70,1:27:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's all anybody can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.70,1:27:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to start by saying how much I respect and appreciate
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.04,1:28:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and care about both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.58,1:28:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very puzzled and confused today by your talk
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.44,1:28:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,on what is absolute truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.78,1:28:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and especially when you said that...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.94,1:28:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk on what?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.96,1:28:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What was absolute truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.72,1:28:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,About saying that campuses have replaced the great books
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.74,1:28:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,by teaching Herbert Marcuse,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.96,1:28:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that the military has been banned from campuses,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.12,1:28:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that patriotism is not okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.84,1:28:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that ethics and morality are not taught.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.20,1:28:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all Marcuse, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.62,1:28:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not true about campus life.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.24,1:28:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not absolute truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.84,1:28:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true about campus life.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.92,1:28:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,About academic life.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.42,1:28:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,About academic life.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.60,1:28:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not academia.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.48,1:28:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's a gross distortion of what occurs in academia.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.06,1:28:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the Duke choir was not attacked
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.22,1:28:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and thrown off the stage?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.68,1:28:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidents occur, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.26,1:28:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we're talking about, incidents.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.72,1:28:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are millions of students.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.74,1:28:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There are thousands of ROTC programs around campus.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.64,1:28:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The great books are taught on every major campus
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.14,1:28:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in America, including Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.86,1:28:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.34,1:29:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.68,1:29:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.32,1:29:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, great, then that's not absolute truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.42,1:29:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.66,1:29:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.28,1:29:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that the level of academia calibrated at certain things
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.35,1:29:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in 1955, it calibrates at a different thing right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.13,1:29:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to defend academia.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.97,1:29:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not criticizing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.86,1:29:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying it once calibrated to very high,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.16,1:29:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it does not calibrate high now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.12,1:29:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.00,1:29:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you just made statements about what occurs on campus
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.86,1:29:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.22,1:29:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't corroborate.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.54,1:29:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just perhaps examples of it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.90,1:29:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We should let go of the examples.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.40,1:29:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I could just give you the calibration.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.52,1:29:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care myself personally
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.48,1:29:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with the calibration of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.10,1:29:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.94,1:29:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what the calibration level was of universities
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.98,1:29:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when I went to them in Wisconsin.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.24,1:30:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know what the calibration of leading universities are today.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.36,1:30:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know what the calibration of the presidents
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.50,1:30:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of some very leading colleges are now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.64,1:30:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's also a list of 50 that calibrate still at 440 through ISI.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.96,1:30:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get a list of 50.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.56,1:30:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you aware that ISI is a publishing company that's owned
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.46,1:30:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,by the Unification Church?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.80,1:30:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's correct, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.00,1:30:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.98,1:30:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.28,1:30:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Great to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.62,1:30:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.16,1:30:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.04,1:30:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.70,1:30:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to sign my book.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.96,1:30:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.36,1:31:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just come for a blessing to say, to express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.78,1:31:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.24,1:31:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think we're a little short on time,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.72,1:31:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm just going to keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.12,1:31:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.62,1:31:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.92,1:31:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about how best to be of service to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.36,1:31:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And most recently, that's taken the form of career choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.34,1:31:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it matter what we do for a living as long as it's not like,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.68,1:31:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, making the choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.22,1:31:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think as long as it's integrous and you feel it serves both yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.62,1:31:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the world, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.92,1:31:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a certain, I mean, is it of equal service to the world
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.06,1:31:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a high-calibrating gas service attendant or to be a psychotherapist
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.50,1:31:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,who reaches more people?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.36,1:31:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it wouldn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.80,1:31:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.76,1:31:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.06,1:32:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bad psychotherapist out there and good gas station attendants.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.82,1:32:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.04,1:32:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.24,1:32:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.48,1:32:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.54,1:32:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.86,1:32:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.16,1:32:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.36,1:32:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You just came to say thank you and that's for picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.98,1:32:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.32,1:32:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're short on time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.84,1:32:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.30,1:32:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.84,1:32:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.14,1:32:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.52,1:32:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.03,1:32:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Be ready to fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.28,1:32:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.00,1:32:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.24,1:32:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as far as the gentleman's criticism of my criticism.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.84,1:32:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself experienced exactly what I talked about.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.14,1:32:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I experienced it from the chairman of the Department of Social,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.12,1:33:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Science in a completely incongruent manner in the middle of a graduation.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.09,1:33:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly came through with a political meme and I thought what the hell is he saying that
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.57,1:33:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,for in the middle of a graduation exercise?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.20,1:33:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So there was a meme, a brainwashed meme slipped in between something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.36,1:33:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So that told me the reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.70,1:33:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The hair went up because I intuit it's indoctrination.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.30,1:33:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't educational.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.04,1:33:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This was to brainstorm the person, the people you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.40,1:33:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I took that as an insult to the integrity of the student body and to me as a parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.63,1:33:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't send my child to be indoctrinated.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.03,1:33:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent her to be educated.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.99,1:33:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you for the indoctrination.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.95,1:33:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.09,1:34:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you had a resentment, so did I.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.60,1:34:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.42,1:34:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.80,1:34:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been coming here for three and a half years.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.66,1:34:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.78,1:34:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The question I have is you've talked in the past pretty highly about the business world
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.52,1:34:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and the standard of living it created allowing us to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.82,1:34:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is what wisdom or advice do you have as I'm trying to figure out how
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.02,1:34:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to communicate these concepts and your knowledge to the business world?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.38,1:34:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you just be that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.96,1:34:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good business.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.62,1:34:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, we calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.88,1:34:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget what you said.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.70,1:34:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated Wal-Mart very high, long before it was popular to not Wal-Mart, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.26,1:34:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.00,1:34:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sam and I conversed.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.74,1:34:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was attracted by his basic integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.58,1:34:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think we calibrated about, I forget, 380 or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.82,1:34:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in the business world, which is usually a little over 200, 204,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.26,1:34:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so if I come out at 380, it was rather astonishing, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.86,1:34:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And so he and I corresponded back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.53,1:34:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as the collapse of Western civilization, I have good news.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.87,1:35:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have good news.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.97,1:35:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have good news.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.77,1:35:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The good news is that Western civilization can only collapse down to like the mid to
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.05,1:35:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,low 300s.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.27,1:35:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And at that point, it interfaces with the business world, the banking world, the world
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.55,1:35:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of integrity, the world of 20-books goods for a $20 bill, and it can't crash any lower
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.55,1:35:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.55,1:35:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.55,1:35:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So the world is going to be held up by Wal-Marts in the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.73,1:35:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.73,1:35:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.73,1:35:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, with relativism, they will forfeit truth, but they won't expect a 10 for a 20.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.26,1:35:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a level of reality below which society is not going to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.95,1:35:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Business, commerce, banking, the law, even the structure of local government, police
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.47,1:35:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,departments.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.47,1:36:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not going to go down below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.27,1:36:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot believe America could go below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.05,1:36:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.53,1:36:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.95,1:36:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.17,1:36:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.27,1:36:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.57,1:36:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.61,1:36:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.81,1:36:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.35,1:36:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.53,1:36:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.73,1:36:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.77,1:36:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.83,1:36:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.91,1:36:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.97,1:36:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mafia would have to take over the entire country to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.75,1:36:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the basic structure of reality is going to hold up the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.91,1:36:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, am I saying this true?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.17,1:36:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying it's true, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.15,1:36:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll put up with all that BS unless it interferes with the reality of business.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.47,1:36:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it begins to affect the stock price, they're going to cut out that BS.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.41,1:36:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is a floor underneath how far
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.71,1:36:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of consciousness of our society will go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.72,1:36:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And they will not allow it to go beyond a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.34,1:36:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is a certain safeguard.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.46,1:36:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So that which is maligned by the politically correct people,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.54,1:36:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in the end is going to be their savior.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.20,1:36:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if it wasn't for the business world, they'd all be out of a job, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.76,1:36:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't be paying nutty professors $60,000 a year to be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.91,1:37:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't get away with that business.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.59,1:37:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine a guy, a nutty professor,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.87,1:37:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,saying 9-11 never happened and the Holocaust never happened
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.29,1:37:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of a business conference?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.99,1:37:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then expecting to get paid $10,000 for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.07,1:37:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.25,1:37:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a certain reality base that the whole structure of our society serves.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.21,1:37:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So by participating in society, by all contributing,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.95,1:37:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,paying our income taxes, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.67,1:37:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we provided a solid floor below which the Western world will not go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.50,1:37:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.38,1:37:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In your book, Power vs. Force, you had mentioned it took you a long time
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.20,1:37:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to figure out how to articulate and communicate your concepts.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.38,1:37:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just thinking along that line, as I've been here,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.82,1:37:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,this is my 15th time and I'm, I guess, a slow learner,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.66,1:37:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm trying to articulate these concepts to business people
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.44,1:37:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm trying to be who I am, obviously, and that's all I can be,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.28,1:38:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but conceptually I'm trying to figure out how do I communicate these to the business world.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.88,1:38:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Research shows that integrity wins in the marketplace.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.26,1:38:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's not, you don't have to advertise the integrity,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.12,1:38:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,all you have to do is be it, be it, be the integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.07,1:38:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's my favorite automobile insurance company?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.88,1:38:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Geico?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.52,1:38:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Geico, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.20,1:38:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I think they ought to calibrate the consciousness level of their advertising.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.28,1:38:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I do too.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.78,1:38:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of companies sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.62,1:38:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sell themselves short.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.92,1:38:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.48,1:38:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that fat guy that was a, he had a blue fairy costume on?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.08,1:38:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,MSN, yep, MSN.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.60,1:38:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God, MSN.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.72,1:38:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,MSN?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.20,1:38:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know what MSN stood for.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.14,1:38:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, MSN.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.32,1:38:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's these three letters and here's a chubby butterfly guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.96,1:38:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it supposed to be a comedy?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.38,1:38:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.38,1:38:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they played it 30, 40 times a day, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.92,1:39:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's what I call negative advertising.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.40,1:39:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The irritation value, if I hear one, there's a certain bank whose name I want,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.76,1:39:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't mention.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.25,1:39:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They will advertise it, and the minute they get through advertising it,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.31,1:39:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,they will rerun the ad again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.07,1:39:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I guess they get paid for so many times a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.69,1:39:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.61,1:39:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would like to see the application of consciousness research in business
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.29,1:39:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,for the welfare and the happiness of everybody,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.57,1:39:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,including the viewers of their television ads.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.97,1:39:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And other TV ads are so clever, so clever, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.81,1:39:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.25,1:39:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can see the heart in them and the humor in them.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.57,1:39:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.15,1:39:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And immediately you feel like a friend of that company.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.97,1:39:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.75,1:39:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So my object,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.79,1:39:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the advertising would be to make every viewer become a friend of my company
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.75,1:39:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and let them know that we're a friend of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.29,1:39:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you get a warm, you know, like J-E-L-L-O.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.22,1:39:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.00,1:39:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.80,1:39:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I left the seven inches of snow in Wisconsin behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.02,1:39:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.80,1:39:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you remember the dancing cigarette package in J-E-L-L-O?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.70,1:40:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We incorporated it into part of our family.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.80,1:40:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,J-E-L-L-O.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.20,1:40:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, ho, ho.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.02,1:40:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.34,1:40:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a wonderful, lovely day.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.96,1:40:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And we tried to fulfill our, you know, to the best that we can.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.76,1:40:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't claim perfection.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.26,1:40:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't claim perfection.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.00,1:40:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We try with the best endeavor to fulfill, answer the questions
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.20,1:40:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and to be the most that we can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.46,1:40:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So all of us here fulfill our obligation to God by becoming potential of that we could be,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.74,1:40:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,by the best of our ability.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.52,1:40:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't ask anything more of anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.62,1:40:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you run as fast as you could run?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.46,1:40:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.42,1:40:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we're not all born with giant legs.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.35,1:40:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.35,1:40:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So we thank thee, O Lord, for the wonderment, for the blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.33,1:40:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a prayer, this congregation of people itself is a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.86,1:41:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And we thank you for revealing that this is the tale that is actually wagging the dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.50,1:41:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That this particular group has an impact on the consciousness level of all of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.62,1:41:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for which we give thanks to thee, O Lord, and amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.10,1:41:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory be to thee, O Lord, amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.67,1:42:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory and excelsis to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.42,1:42:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
